C CODE
------------------------------------

#include<stdio.h>
int main(){
  printf("Hello Shreyasi");
  return 0;
}

--------------------------------------
COMMANDS 
vi filename.c – Open or create a C file in Vi editor

Press i – Enter insert mode to start typing code

Press Esc – Exit insert mode after typing

:w – Save the file

:q – Quit the editor

:wq – Save and quit Vi editor

gcc filename.c -o outputname – Compile the C program

./outputname – Run the compiled program

clear – Clear the terminal screen

ls – Check if files like .c and compiled output exist
